title: * Minimum required Android version is now 2.2 instead of 4.0. Some features…
message:
* Minimum required Android version is now 2.2 instead of 4.0. Some features (like making the Panel transparent) are not available on older versions of Android, though.
* Russian translation
* Dutch translation
* The wallpaper can now be changed from the Preferences screen.
* Bugfix: "Panel opacity" option was shown by default in Preferences screen when "Show Panel" was disabled.
* Bugfix: The app sometimes crashed with an OutOfMemoryError while blurring the wallpaper. When this happens the crash will now be supressed and the wallpaper will be darkened instead of blurred when the Dash is opened (like what happens to live wallpapers).

title: Bugfix: When calculating the dominant colour of grayscale images, the…
message:
Bugfix: When calculating the dominant colour of grayscale images, the transparency setting was ignored.
Bugfix: The Dash close button was in the wrong location when the Launcher had been resized.
Bugfix: The default setting for the Launcher width was too high.
Bugfix: When Ubuntu Launcher is set as the default home screen, and the back button is pressed, it will no longer quit.
